Description: containerd runtime shim for Firecracker microVMs
 Firecracker-containerd provides a containerd runtime shim that allows
 containerd to manage Firecracker microVMs using the OCI runtime spec.
 .
 It enables running container workloads inside Firecracker VMs with
 minimal overhead, providing strong isolation with container-like
 developer experience.
 .
 This package includes:
  * firecracker-containerd daemon
  * firecracker-agent binary
  * Default configuration and systemd service
  * CNI plugins for VM networking
 .
 Part of the Mikrom platform (https://www.mikrom.es)
